  "original_title": "Dedicated filling stations for delivery trucks",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dedicated filling stations for delivery trucks",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Minister of Trade, Commerce, and Food Security announced that dedicated filling stations will be named to issue fuel for State Sector & Private Sector delivery trucks that transport goods to and from the Economic Centers.",
        "Accordingly, a list of filling stations operated by the Three-Armed Forces will be announced to cater to the 11 dedicated Economic Centers across the country.",
        "Accordingly, the Ratmalana Economic Center will be issued fuel from the Ratmalana Air Force Camp, and the Meegoda Economic Center from the Mattegoda Army Camp.",
        "The Narahenpita Economic Center will be provided fuel from Ratmalana Air Force Base and Matthegoda Engineer Corps Headquarters.",
        "Dambulla Economic Center will be provided fuel from the Sri Lanka Army 53 Division Headquarters complex in Inamaluwa.",
        "Yupun becomes first South Asian to finish 100m below 10 seconds & win"
      ],
